<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-24">

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Rails Typst Examples</h2>

  <p class="mt-12 text-gray-700">
    Below is a list of examples that demonstrate how to use the Rails Typst gem.
  </p>

  <ul class="mt-8 list-disc list-inside">
    <li>
      <%= link_to "Simple", typst_examples_simple_path(format: :pdf), class: "font-semibold hover:underline" %>
      - A simple example that demonstrates how to use the Rails Typst gem.
    </li>
    <li>
      <%= link_to "Simple-Erb", typst_examples_simple_erb_path(format: :pdf), class: "font-semibold hover:underline" %>
      - An example that demonstrates how to use the Rails Typst gem including the use of embedded ruby.
    </li>
    <li>
      <%= link_to "Simple-With-Files", typst_examples_simple_with_files_path(format: :pdf), class: "font-semibold hover:underline" %>
      - An example that demonstrates how to use the Rails Typst gem including the use of additional files.
    </li>
  </ul>

</main>
